WEBVTT

00:07:57.566 --> 00:08:01.201
And that brought me then
to climate justice.

00:08:01.225 --> 00:08:05.384
Climate justice responds
to the moral argument --

00:08:05.408 --> 00:08:07.440
both sides of the moral argument --

00:08:07.464 --> 00:08:09.882
to address climate change.

00:08:09.906 --> 00:08:11.057
First of all,

00:08:11.081 --> 00:08:14.945
to be on the side of those who are
suffering most and are most effected.

00:08:15.294 --> 00:08:16.651
And secondly,

00:08:16.675 --> 00:08:21.676
to make sure that they're not left behind
again, when we start to move

00:08:21.700 --> 00:08:24.509
and start to address climate change
with climate action,

00:08:24.533 --> 00:08:26.055
as we are doing.

00:08:27.834 --> 00:08:30.628
In our very unequal world today,